There are no references to tvnserver.exe (or tvnserver) anywhere in the Island codebase across all zeroabstraction repositories (browser, apps, cloud, endpoint-agent, infrastructure, network).

tvnserver.exe is the TightVNC server process, a third-party remote desktop tool. It is not bundled with, referenced by, or related to the Island browser or installer. If you're seeing it alongside Island processes on a machine, it was installed separately
